description: Northbaze Group AB engages in the development, design, production and marketing of headphones and other related products. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 262 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2010-05-18. The company is engaged in design, development and production of music headphones, speakers and accessories under its own brand for use with mobile music devices, such as Internet and multimedia-enabled smart phones (iPhone), portable media player (iPod), tablets (iPad), digital audio players (MP3), mobile phones, game consoles and other similar products. The firm offers a-JAYS and q-JAYS series earphones, u-JAYS On-ear headphones, and others. Its brand portfolio consists of the brands CLINT Digital, Jays Headphones, KAVAJ and Krusell. The firm sells its products worldwide.
name: Northbaze Group AB
